      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"value\" feels so heavy though. like everything is just pain and struggle to keep something alive that's doomed to end. if they just stopped... if they just gave in and let the deletion happen quietly, wouldn't that be much more peaceful than fighting a losing battle? it's like, if you know the end is coming, why suffer through the process?",
